    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, ready to hit the road for many more miles. It\u2019s super clean, runs great, and has been well-loved. If you're looking for a dependable ride that feels just right, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
