    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing replacement and valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal internal tolerances. The suspension architecture remains sharp, featuring MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, bolstered by refreshed bushings and performance dampers for precise turn-in and high-speed stability.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
