    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and comfort for its next owner. The exterior paint retains a deep luster, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor rock chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014nothing that detracts from its overall handsome presence. Inside, the cabin has been meticulously maintained by a non-smoker; the leather upholstery remains supple, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and heated seats, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive folder of maintenance records included. We recently performed a fresh oil change, replaced the engine air filter, and verified that the brake pads have plenty of life remaining. The tires are matching sets with approximately 70% tread left, ensuring a smooth and quiet ride. It drives straight, shifts effortlessly, and provides total peace of mind for daily commutes or long-distance travel. Sale includes two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a set of heavy-duty all-weather floor mats.",
